{"tid":388489,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[退出娛樂圈?] 陳冠希推出新歌\"爽\" MV 古靈精怪","createTime":"2017-09-05T13:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T22:26:00.000Z","uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3889bed24f9e4ce98b23d4719693a4d2ca18af","tid":388489,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8bjXN-FEFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS8bjXN-FEFg&d=gJGV%2FGGIthcadGnvJRRIY%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=bd596372\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8bjXN-FEFg</a><br />\n早前陳冠希（Edison）透過IG同大家公佈「很快就有2017年暑假最爽的一首歌」，並透露新曲叫《爽》。由於Edison好多年都冇推出新曲，所以大家都非常期待。新曲終於喺日前與網上發布，MV中只有Edison一個人跟著音樂搖動，再加埋老土嘅動畫效果，網友睇完後都表示睇到好尷尬，仲睇得出佢真係好爽！<br />\n<br />\n另外，首歌Edison係用普通話去唱，MV又冇字幕，根本聽唔明佢唱緊咩。不過就算首歌有幾多負評都好，Edison都似乎不太在乎，始終有新聞總比無新聞好。<br />\n<br />\n佢係新歌上載同一日，同MC JIN一齊開LIVE做宣傳，係節目中Edison形容「Hip Hop是一個生活，是一個文化，我怎麼穿衣服，怎麼跟女朋友做愛，全部都係HIP HOP。」真係睇得出Edison好積極咁爭取曝光率。<br />\n<br />\n之前成班連登仔話佢一早退出咗娛樂圈, 啲記者仲訪問佢係唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事就話佢退出, 得閒就靠娛樂圈攞曝光率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無敵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57af358741d8e2fa5fb932b9556f0b4b04bf0d60","tid":388489,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef5c0cc5fb9d3a2aecd4b7f4efa5ae348311f0d","tid":388489,"uid":8557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"怎麼跟女朋友做愛<br />\n<br />\n乜撚呀希哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723b60c6a23e69d376ca5abd235bc91c5fd34a46","tid":388489,"uid":1255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"個MV好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\